@model int


<div class="container py-5 text-center">

    <div class="checkout-steps mb-5 justify-content-center" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div class="step done"><div class="step-num"><i class="bi bi-check"></i></div><span class="step-label">Cart</span></div>
        <div class="step-line done"></div>
        <div class="step done"><div class="step-num"><i class="bi bi-check"></i></div><span class="step-label">Checkout</span></div>
        <div class="step-line done"></div>
        <div class="step active"><div class="step-num"><i class="bi bi-check-all"></i></div><span class="step-label">Confirmation</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-4">
        <i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success" style="font-size: 6rem;"></i>
    </div>

    <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-3">Thank You For Your Order!</h1>
    <p class="lead text-muted mb-5">
        تم استلام طلبك بنجاح، وجاري تجهيزه للشحن. سنتواصل معك قريباً لتأكيد ميعاد التوصيل.
    </p>

    <div class="card mx-auto shadow-sm border-0" style="max-width: 450px; background-color: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 15px;">
        <div class="card-body py-4">
            <p class="text-muted mb-2 fw-bold text-uppercase" style="letter-spacing: 1px;">Order Tracking ID</p>
            <h2 class="fw-bold mb-0" style="color: var(--accent, #dc3545);">#@Model</h2>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-5 d-flex justify-content-center gap-3">
        <a href="/Home/Index" class="btn btn-outline-dark px-4 py-3 fw-bold rounded-pill">
            <i class="bi bi-arrow-left me-2"></i> Continue Shopping
        </a>
    </div>
</div>